column5: My brother is doing an ad presentation, he's on the Gold Coast and needs a pic of a chinook/king in action...leaping. Anyone got one handy? Please and thank you.
try going to google images and put in salmon jumping  lot's of photos. I understand if you want something from us but if it's a last resort kind of thing go to google. Hope this helps
here are a couple of chinnies in 'action' but i am not sure that's what you meant.
That's a super pic Raf, thanks! I think he wants a leaper for the purposes of the ad.
sorry roy.. one day i will learn to use my superpowers for the forces of good and not evil.  a pic of a leper king may be tough.
This is the best one I have of one jumping.

If I can remember Roy, I have a bunch at home.  They are the old fashioned paper kind, you know 35 mm days.  I took them when I was living out west.  A bunch of salmon swimming up the water falls.  Awsome experience to see.
